               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, Asmat Prayers</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="178r"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተግሣጽ ለኵሉ: ወአስተናሥኦ: ምግባር:ፍካሬ: ዘጻድቃን: ወዘኃጥአን: መዝሙር: ዘዳዊት።</incipit>
                </msItem>
               </msContents>
